node.text:
Old world craftsmanship meets new world technology. Originally designed as a hand carved balsa plug in the hills of East Tennessee, the Chick Magnet was one of @andymorganfishing’s best kept secrets for years until now. Our product development team worked closely with original lure designer Marion Tipton and Andy himself to perfect everything down to the finest details. Not an easy task, but the results speak for themselves. The Chick Magnet is a modernization of the most legendary handcrafted flatsided plug in existence.

#StrikeKing #TieOneOn #ChickMagnet #hardlure #bassfishing

node.title: The Origin of the Chick Magnet

node.text:
Introducing the NEW Andy Montgomery Skip’ N Buzz. This game-changing lure is specifically built to help anglers target out-of-reach fish in places where few baits will go. The legendary Strike King buzzbait, with a new design twist, is reshaping the way anglers find and catch fish.

To engineer this innovative design, Strike King turned to arguably the most proficient skipping and pitching angler on the water, Bass Pro Tour veteran @andymontgomeryfishing. For two of his tour-level wins in his career — on Lake Norman and Smith Lake — the Blacksburg, SC native credits his ability to skip a lure into the dark recesses underneath a dock to target tournament-winning fish.

#StrikeKing #StrikeKingLureCompany #BassProTour #icast #Andymontgomery #fishing #buzzbait

[Episode 4] @mark_zona_fishing and @kevinvandamfishing are reunited on the water for the first time in years to put on a beatdown of epic proportions on Lake St. Clair 💥 

Follow @greghackneyfishing's journey as he tackles one of the greatest bass fishing lakes in the nation and learn how he got into the sport we all love.

What's something new you learned from this episode?

Air date: 𝐌𝐨𝐧𝐝𝐚𝐲, 𝐉𝐮𝐧𝐞 𝟐𝟖 𝐚𝐭 𝟕𝐩𝐦 𝐄𝐓 𝐨𝐧 𝐈𝐆𝐓𝐕 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐘𝐨𝐮𝐓𝐮𝐛𝐞.

Reunited on the water for the first time in years. @mark_zona_fishing phones a friend and puts on a beatdown of epic proportions with @kevinvandamfishing on Lake St. Clair! Go behind the scenes and see how Z prepares to film a fishing show and hear how bass fishing has changed his life.

@greghackneyfishing continues his quest to qualify for the @bass_nation Classic at Lake Fork. Follow his journey as he tackles one of the greatest bass fishing lakes and learn how he got into the sport we all love.

#StrikeKing #Lews #KingsOfBass #bassfishing #Bassmaster #MLF

[𝐍𝐄𝐖 𝐄𝐏𝐈𝐒𝐎𝐃𝐄] 𝐊𝐢𝐧𝐠𝐬 𝐨𝐟 𝐁𝐚𝐬𝐬: 𝐄𝐩𝐢𝐬𝐨𝐝𝐞 𝟒
Air Date: Monday, June 28 at 7pm ET
IGTV + YouTube Premiere 🎥

It's go time for @greghackneyfishing. Follow his tourney prep for the @bass_nation Elites on Lake Fork and see the dedication it takes to become one of the bass fishing greats.

He spends countless hours crafting content and broadcasting bass fishing on ZONA's Awesome Fishing Show and for the Bassmaster tournament trail. See how @mark_zona_fishing balances it all with quality time on the water.

#StrikeKing #KingsOfBass

node.text:
[New Video ➡️ Link in bio!]

"𝑊ℎ𝑒𝑛 𝑦𝑜𝑢 𝑔𝑒𝑡 𝑔𝑜𝑜𝑑 𝑝𝑒𝑜𝑝𝑙𝑒 𝑡𝑜𝑔𝑒𝑡ℎ𝑒𝑟 𝑎𝑛𝑑 𝑦𝑜𝑢 𝑠𝑡𝑎𝑟𝑡 𝑐𝑜𝑚𝑚𝑢𝑛𝑖𝑐𝑎𝑡𝑖𝑛𝑔 𝑤𝑒𝑙𝑙, 𝑦𝑜𝑢 𝑐𝑎𝑛 𝑑𝑜 𝑎 𝑙𝑜𝑡 𝑜𝑓 𝑔𝑜𝑜𝑑." 

MLF angler and U.S. Army veteran Jeff Sprague is joined on the water by Jerod Napier - 20 year U.S. Navy Senior Chief Petty Officer and Purple Heart recipient - in support of Casting Freedom. 🇺🇸 

Like and subscribe as we share the camaraderie and community that fishing inspires while on the water with our nation's heroes via partnerships between the Lew's American Hero program and groups like Casting Freedom, Warriors Heart and others devoted to supporting our veterans and first responders.

node.text:
Old world craftsmanship meets new world technology. Originally designed as a hand carved balsa plug in the hills of East Tennessee, the Chick Magnet was one of @andymorganfishing’s best kept secrets for years until now. Our product development team worked closely with original lure designer Marion Tipton and Andy himself to perfect everything down to the finest details. Not an easy task, but the results speak for themselves. The Chick Magnet is a modernization of the most legendary handcrafted flatsided plug in existence.

#StrikeKing #TieOneOn #ChickMagnet #hardlure #bassfishing

@kevinvandamfishing @andymorganfishing @jeffspraguefishing @roseoutdoors

node.text: Our very own @andymontgomeryfishing is not only an expert angler, but also an Olympic Long Jump gold medalist! 🥇😂 Andy jumped himself all the way up the leaderboard today with 42lb 4oz of Lake Champlain bass and is sitting in 5th place! Go Andy🙌🏼🔥 #teamstrikeking

Oneida Lake was a bit stingy last week during the Bassmaster Opens. That didn't stop Team Strike King from making appearances in the Top 10! Here's what worked in Upstate NY:

- Strike King Pro Model Series Crankbait
- 4.25-inch Strike King Dream Shot
- 1/4- or 3/8-ounce Strike King Tour Grade Drop Shot Weights
- Strike King 3X ElazTech Baby Z Too Soft Jerkbait
- Strike King Rage Swimmer Swimbait

📸 @bass_nation 

#StrikeKing #Bassmaster #OneidaLake #Bassfishing
